  "title": "Senior / Physiotherapist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in managing the physiotherapy services</li>\n  <li>Evaluate patient as a basis for planning and implementing an appropriate treatment programme</li>\n  <li>Administer therapeutic interventions to alleviate impairment or functional limitations and to maximise optimal recovery</li>\n  <li>Initiate discharge planning and recommend appropriate discharge therapy programme</li>\n  <li>Maintain clear, appropriate and accurate documentation of all treatments in a timely manner</li>\n  <li>Ensure that the referring sources are updated appropriately of the patient's progress in a timely manner</li>\n  <li>Activate cross referral to the other Rehab disciplines when appropriate, in consultation with the referring physician</li>\n  <li>Perform any other duties as may be assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Full AHPC registration</li>\n  <li>Degree/ Diploma in Physiotherapy</li>\n</ul>",
